BR_text.BRsummary: Integrate the new force reload behaviour for events/logs/assets
BR_text.BRdescription:
<denchmark-h:h3>Describe the bug</denchmark-h>
 
 The UI does not update charts because of the new caching feature, this is the intended behaviour, but it should use the --force flag to force fetch/update the asset when the runs are not finished.
 <denchmark-h:h3>To Reproduce</denchmark-h>
 
 Any page on the artifacts/dashboards of an operation that is still running.
 <denchmark-h:h3>Expected behavior</denchmark-h>
 
 
 Use the new --force flag when runs are not finished.
 
 <denchmark-h:h3>Environment</denchmark-h>
 
 1.0.96
